    "text": "While regulation and consumer pressure may appear to be the most serious issues being faced by GreenTech, the most pressing issue of concern to GreenTech is actually the rapid rise in supplier prices. Without an abatement of supplier costs, rising raw material prices will cause GreenTech to realize a loss in profit margins (and subsequently not only not having enough funds available to invest in new technologies and improvements) as a direct result of continued increases in supplier price.",
    "children": [
