    "text": "This new phase of growth involves choosing between two two different alternatives. One way is by growing through related diversification and expanding into industries that are similar in some way to the company's current businesses. Another way is to diversify into completely new industries outside of the company's current business model, for example, growing into financial technology (fintech) or growing into the digital health care industry",
